comments: THE BEST teacher at Seminole State, hands down. She made Literature interesting to me, and she was very helpful. Seminole state is VERY lucky to have her here.

She like to read aloud a lot which doesn\'t bother me.There is a lot of writing, but it is simple. I don\'t think she even really reads your papers. Easy A if you go to class and do the assignments. Very laid back in grading work.

Mrs. Laudani is an amazing teacher! She is a middle school teacher. And she does read the stories and poems to you in class. But she gives you multiple chances to re-write and email in your papers. She really is there to help and wants you to achieve. If you have the choice, take her. She\'s wonderful!
Middle School Teacher trying to teach college level classes. Needs to stay in middle school.
